8. Beverage:juice is in the middle
9. Nationality:spanish is on the far left
10. Cigar:bolivar is on the left or right of Pet:lizard
11. Pet:hamsters is on the left or right of Cigar:fonseca
12. Cigar:ebonymaster == Beverage:7up
13. Nationality:brazilian == Cigar:old-henry
14. Nationality:spanish is on the left or right of Color:ebony
15. Cigar:bolivar is on the left or right of Beverage:almond-milk

